{"tid":512912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國被發現賣石油給北韓　川普：感到非常失望","createTime":"2017-12-29T03:55:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T13:48:14.000Z","uid":76115,"like":186,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"fe822f63944a48570e3448fbe94e124272f64cb2","tid":512912,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T03:55:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171229/1268291/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171229%2F1268291%2F&d=wTNcWpiBTO2ik9uJSyl1EfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=004ffa54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171229%2F1268291%2F&h=0bf4a53e\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171229/1268291/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171229/640_3628cb519cd89d520c2fd8854cbdfb41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171229%2F640_3628cb519cd89d520c2fd8854cbdfb41.jpg&h=09c9dfb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國衛星拍到中國暗中販賣石油給北韓。 翻攝網路<br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普對「中國容許石油進入北韓」，感到非常失望，認為此舉妨礙達成「友好的方案」，難以解決北韓核武危機。<br />\n<br />\n川普周四在Twitter發文：「抓個正著。對中國容許石油進入北韓非常失望，若此繼續發生，北韓問題永不會有友好的解決方案！」<br />\n <br />\n美國間諜衛星拍到中國船隻過去3個月非法售賣石油給北韓的照片，南韓報章也報導中國船隻非法在海上把石油輸送到北韓船隻上。中國周四回應說，中國船隻從沒有違反聯合國制裁令，把石油賣給北韓。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"ba3fabe7a42f24d6e985a85b403f4c68dbadad31","tid":512912,"uid":59898,"like":52,"dislike":2,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T03:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 侵侵怒屌支那"},{"pid":"453fe6d407e6d0463c6dd448c31287f3e94338d5","tid":512912,"uid":51717,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T03:56:56.000Z","msg":"Set緊個局?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f78b6e9717b4a